description: Redevelopment of the site to provide 99 market residential units and 59 affordable housing units, 542 square metres of Class A1, A2, A3 or D1 use within four buildings of 7 - 17 storeys in height together with the provision of public and private open space, new access road, basement car parking and associated hard and soft landscaping.  S73 application to vary conditions 3, 4, 7, 9, 10, 11, 13, 14 and 20 (in order to allow a phased development) attached to planning permission PP/08/01214, dated 11 December 2008, for: Redevelopment of the site to provide 99 market residential units and 59 affordable housing units, 542 square metres of Class A1, A2, A3 or D1 use within four buildings of 7 - 17 storeys in height together with the provision of public and private open space, new access road, basement car parking and associated hard and soft landscaping
